Product.Name: Tommee Tippee Ctn Transition Cup
Product.SupplyLimitMessage: 'Tommee Tippee Ctn Transition Cup' has a supply limit of 36. The quantity in your cart has been reduced accordingly. To purchase a larger quantity, please contact us on 1800 000 610. Please note we do not supply trade orders.
Product.RichDescription:
Designed for use from 4 months, this small Transition Cup with a 150ml capacity, is the perfect choice for your baby?s first sips. Up until this point they?ve been used to breast or bottle, so introducing a cup is an important step in their drinking journey.
To help the transition go smoothly, this cup features a super soft, Tommee Tippee  teat for a familiar breast or bottle feel for those very first sips.  Once comfortable with the removable, easy-grip handles on the coloured cup base then you can progress onto the soft sippee cup spout.
The offset nature of the soft spout encourages a more natural cup drinking action by changing the angle they drink from, ready for a progression onto a full sippee cup.

Products.RichDescription:
Heinz Baby Basics Snack Pod Non-Spill is ideal for fruit + snacks.

The Heinz Baby Basics non-spill snack pod is perfect for on the go snacking with a lot less mess.

This snack pod is perfect for small and large snacks, including fruit. Its slatted silicone lid is soft and flexible making snacks easy to grab when on the go whilst avoiding messy spills. The built-in travel lid helps to lock in freshness and avoid mess when inside your bag! Just simply pop open the lid when the snacks are needed again. The easy grip handles enable your baby to grip hold of the snack pod while making snacking on-the-go in the pushchair, car seat or highchair a breeze!

Dishwasher safe (Top rack only).

Steriliser safe.

- BPA Bisphenol-A Free.

- Easy access.

- Keep fresh no mess lid.

- Easy to grip handles.

Products.RichDescription:
Huggies nappies are Huggies softest nappy featuring cotton-like softness to gently hug your baby, suitable for boys & girls. The Ultimate nappy range features silky soft sides providing superior protection from leaks and red marks around the legs.

Pack Count: 96 nappies.

Size 2 (Infant) Nappy Size Guide: Baby Weight 4 - 8kg.
Huggies Infant Nappies are clinically proven to help prevent nappy rash, and are endorsed by the Australian College of Midwives as the preferred choice for baby.

The Ultimate Infant nappy features:
- Up to 12 hours leakage protection, perfect for day and night usage.
- A wetness indicator which turns from yellow to blue when wet making it easier to know when to change.

- Same absorbent performance for both boys & girls.


Huggies Ultimate disposable nappies are Huggies softest nappy featuring cotton-like softness to gently hug your baby. The Ultimate nappy range features silky soft sides providing superior protection from leaks and red marks around the legs as well as a soft and stretchy waistband for all round protection. The Breathe Dry cover makes the Ultimate nappy and diapers range Huggies most breathable and has been clinically proven to help prevent nappy rash. With up to 12 hours protection and a DryTouch layer, that instantly absorbs wetness springing back dry the Ultimate nappy range for Infants is ideal both as a day and night nappy. Huggies Ultimate Infant nappies are ideally sized for babies weighing up to 4-8KG. Huggies infant nappies are endorsed by the Australian College of Midwives as the preferred choice for baby.

Huggies Ultimate disposable nappy range is available in the following sizes; 1 Newborn (up to 5kg), 2 Infant (4 - 8KG), 3 Crawler (6 - 11KG), 4 Toddler (10 - 15KG), and 5 Walker (13 - 18KG).
